#message:0A:081
{
[Style Left]
I love composing music.[BR]
[Pause 10]The legendary writer, [SaveColor][Color:02]Toadofsky[RestoreColor][BR]
told me to come here to gather[BR]
inspiration for my pieces.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I do suppose music can be quite[BR]
romantic.[BR]
Horns are a wonderful misstress.
[Wait][End]
}

#message:0A:082
{
[Style Left]
How do you do, Mario?[BR]
[Pause 5]Toadofsky was right in saying I[BR]
should come to the Love Hotel.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I've gotten a lot of brilliant ideas,[BR]
just watching couples coming and[BR]
going from this sacred locale.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
My heartbeat is like a metronome.[BR]
[Wave]Badump. Badump. [HEART][/fx]
[Wait][End]
}

